  "texts": [
    "In this experiment, our methods deliver superior performance under the generalization setting.",
    "For instance, our method significantly improves various evaluation metrics compared to GMPNN-CS in experiments conducted on the dataset divided according to the structure.",
    "Specifically, the ACC improves by 5.65%, the AUC improves by 4.03%, the F1 improves by 8.13%, the Prec improves by 5.87%, the Rec improves by 8.25%, and the AP improves by 5.33%.",
    "It indicates that extracting only key substructure information cannot improve the model's drug interaction prediction performance.",
    "In this case, additional fusion of information from other sources is required."
  ],
